/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   VUSL V17 — Optimized Multi-Pack Game Launcher

   Changes from V16:
   ⓐ External tab rebuilt: upload individual files or
      whole folders (webkitdirectory) instead of a
      base-URL + filename-list config. Content is read
      directly into IndexedDB — no network fetch needed.
   ⓑ New uploads merge with existing external games
      instead of overwriting. If new filenames collide
      with already-uploaded ones, a modal asks whether
      to skip duplicates or overwrite them.
   ⓒ External tab moved to the far right of the tab bar
      (pinned via CSS margin-left:auto), Favorites sits
      just before it.
   ⓓ New "Refresh" button — re-runs scanCache() on demand
      so newly-downloaded games show their cached outline
      immediately without needing a full page reload.
   ⓔ Clear Cache now warns separately about external
      uploads, since those can't be re-downloaded from
      GitHub — clearing purges them permanently.
   ⓕ Per-card remove (🗑) for external games only.
   ⓖ Guarded key parsing (packId/filename) against
      filenames/pack ids that might contain ":" by using
      a reserved separator lookup instead of naive split.

   Perf improvements carried over from V16:
   ① cardNodeCache  — O(1) DOM lookups in setCardStatus
   ② renderGrid     — DocumentFragment batch insert
   ③ Search debounce — 120 ms, not every keystroke
   ④ MAX_PAR 25     — two origins → can saturate both
   ⑤ scanCache      — getAllKeys once; Set lookup O(1)
   ⑥ Rescan strategy — tab-focus visibilitychange + manual refresh button
   ⑦ renderStatus   — single cached element refs
════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

